{"tid":2365172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府明日起全天候開放回港易計劃預約系統","createTime":"2021-01-13T14:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T14:31:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f582bd52fab228c4ecb121d8a694bcb5a9bb06d3","tid":2365172,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"政府明日起全天候開放回港易計劃預約系統<br />\n<br />\n政府明日起全天候開放回港易計劃的預約系統，方便市民可隨時預約系統內的名額。<br />\n<br />\n市民可以即時預約明日至本月24日的名額，之後預約系統逢每星期三的零時起，開放下個星期的7天時段名額。政府指，為實施新的預約安排，預約系統會於今晚午夜起更新，將暫停服務約30分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2374678&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d79003c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374678</a>"},{"pid":"c3ce1b29a0741273168ed47e204bc69e686e207c","tid":2365172,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"石家莊：正呀"},{"pid":"918b9efb8afecc9fd3774d2c9c297522323a3849","tid":2365172,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"多謝政府"},{"pid":"7e78b204c1c0602cd0a29951a835306db753758b","tid":2365172,"uid":7524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"準備下一波， 爽"},{"pid":"38d1fb0021e04adb2b3c2546b5078f6771dec428","tid":2365172,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"回港播毒易計劃"},{"pid":"6da725519a1ae83ae9578bd2321bf1907e75e5fb","tid":2365172,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"公務員永續wfh <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2b5413e69eae16cff8bb259274c2de205ec0bb","tid":2365172,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">第5波靠呢班愛國者喇</sp